### Create a new expense
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Lunch at the cafe",
  "amount": 15.50,
  "category": "Food"
}

### Create another expense
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Monthly subscription",
  "amount": 9.99,
  "category": "Entertainment"
}

### Create a third expense
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Grocery shopping",
  "amount": 45.20,
  "category": "Groceries"
}

### Create a fourth expense
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Movie tickets",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "category": "Entertainment"
}

### Get all expenses for the last month
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses?period=MONTH

### Get all expenses for the last week
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses?period=WEEK

### Get all expenses
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/expenses
